<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1204641-for-those-of-you-who-ve-read-the-catcher">For those of you who&#39;ve read The Catcher Was a Spy:... asking

1- if the book refers to his aliases. How many aliases did he have (and why was one of those an Iranian/Middle Eastern alias, i.e., why did he choose that as opposed to other nationalities)...and also 

2- did he actually speak 7 languages?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1204641'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F34629.The_Catcher_Was_a_Spy">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1204641-for-those-of-you-who-ve-read-the-catcher">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1204641-for-those-of-you-who-ve-read-the-catcher">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/2134856-joe"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1418326984i/2134856._UY100_CR16,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/2134856-joe">Joe</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It doesn&apos;t talk about any aliases and he was somewhat fluent in 3 languages at the most. He could read in 2 or 3 additional languages.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It doesn't talk about any aliases and he was somewhat fluent in 3 languages at the most. He could read in 2 or 3 additional languages.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
